      "s": "Sam's Club has committed to sustainability goals through its Member's Mark private label, targeting 100% sustainably sourced seafood, deforestation-free palm oil, and recyclable/compostable packaging by 2025. The company participates in Walmart's Project Gigaton initiative to reduce or avoid 1 billion metric tons of greenhouse gas emissions by 2030 and has implemented the Zero Depack food waste reduction program across stores. Sustainability efforts are partially commendable but many targets remain aspirational and tied to supplier compliance rather than directly verified third-party certifications.",
