      "s": "<cite index=\"81-2,81-3\">L'Oréal SA contributed $95,996 to campaigns and spent $70,000 on lobbying in the 2024 cycle.</cite> <cite index=\"82-1\">In 2025, L'Oréal SA spent $180,000 lobbying.</cite> The company maintains a bipartisan stance with minimal political donations, focusing primarily on lobbying efforts related to trade, tariffs, and regulatory matters.",
