      "s": "<cite index=\"12-1\">Visa and Visa Foundation make charitable donations and grants to advance the goals and strategic priorities we have set for enabling individuals, businesses, and economies to thrive.</cite> <cite index=\"13-5\">Community giving efforts focus on the needs most relevant to the communities in which we live, work and do business across themes such as access to education, support for vulnerable populations, hunger relief and promotion of good health.</cite> <cite index=\"14-8,14-10\">Grants funded $80 million and Dedicated investments made $120 million in emerging markets helping more women control capital.</cite>",
